BROKERAGE TRANSFER CO., Inc., Plaintiff in Error (defendant below), v. MARYLAND DREDGING & CONTRACTING CO., Defendant in Error (plaintiff below). (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. November 17, 1924.) No. 95. Davis, Wagner, Heater & Holton, of New York City (A. L. Davis, of New York City, of counsel), for plaintiff in error. S. Selig, of New York City, for defendant in error.

Before HOUGH and MANTON, Circuit Judges, and LEARNED HAND, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed, with costs.
